page.title: 07HOUSES.
page.content: 6 people live in semidetached houses.13 people live in houses and 2 people live in bungalows. There are three people whose houses have special features.1 person has got unusual windowsand another person has got patterned windows. The last person has got smugglers tunnels and bottles built in to the wall . That person is Ben and he lives in the Lifeboat Inn. ARTS AND CRAFTS. The bead neaklaces are made of all kinds of different beads and there is loads of black sheeps wool Jumpers and wool mats and leather belts. Also they sell alot of pottery and a lot of lavender. MRS GLOVER.Paints sheels and bookmarks which she sells for CHARITY she also makes butterflies.
